---
// APISecurityChecklist.astro — Quick security checklist for APIs
---
<div class="asc-wrap">
  <h3 class="asc-title">API Security Checklist</h3>
  <div class="asc-cols">
    <div class="asc-col"><span class="asc-hl asc-hl--green">Transport</span><div class="asc-item">☐ TLS 1.3 everywhere</div><div class="asc-item">☐ HSTS header</div><div class="asc-item">☐ No mixed content</div><div class="asc-item">☐ Certificate pinning (mobile)</div></div>
    <div class="asc-col"><span class="asc-hl asc-hl--amber">Auth</span><div class="asc-item">☐ Short-lived tokens (15 min)</div><div class="asc-item">☐ Refresh token rotation</div><div class="asc-item">☐ Rate limit login/register</div><div class="asc-item">☐ Validate all JWT claims</div></div>
    <div class="asc-col"><span class="asc-hl asc-hl--cyan">Input</span><div class="asc-item">☐ Schema validation on all inputs</div><div class="asc-item">☐ Parameterized queries</div><div class="asc-item">☐ Content-Type validation</div><div class="asc-item">☐ Max body size enforced</div></div>
    <div class="asc-col"><span class="asc-hl asc-hl--red">Output</span><div class="asc-item">☐ Never expose stack traces</div><div class="asc-item">☐ Filter response fields by role</div><div class="asc-item">☐ Security headers set</div><div class="asc-item">☐ CORS properly configured</div></div>
  </div>
</div>
<style>
  .asc-wrap{background:linear-gradient(135deg,#0f172a,#1e293b);border-radius:16px;padding:2rem;margin:2rem 0;border:1px solid #334155}
  .asc-title{color:#f1f5f9;font-size:1.15rem;font-weight:700;margin:0 0 1.5rem}
  .asc-cols{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(150px,1fr));gap:10px}
  .asc-col{padding:12px;background:rgba(0,0,0,.2);border-radius:10px;border:1px solid #334155}
  .asc-hl{display:block;font-size:.68rem;font-weight:700;font-family:monospace;margin-bottom:8px}
  .asc-hl--green{color:#4ade80}.asc-hl--amber{color:#f59e0b}.asc-hl--cyan{color:#06b6d4}.asc-hl--red{color:#f87171}
  .asc-item{color:#94a3b8;font-size:.65rem;line-height:1.8}
</style>
